{"tid":2181048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"事實查核實驗室: 撐警群組指控裁判官何俊堯判刑較同類案件輕屬誤導內容","createTime":"2020-08-30T10:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T12:06:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7740f23ef2d5d3398386ddf7587afa4abcf9c2ab","tid":2181048,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/200817-cover-facebook-1_BtD4x_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F200817-cover-facebook-1_BtD4x_1200x0.png&h=a6f45db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www-cdn.factchecklab.org/2020/08/117398229_186585216231093_417318101874655014_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-cdn.factchecklab.org%2F2020%2F08%2F117398229_186585216231093_417318101874655014_n.jpg&h=294eaf9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n<br />\n圖1宣稱把裁判官何俊堯判決的三宗案件跟「同樣案情」的案件對比，然而第一組中，兩宗案件控罪不同、案情性質有別；第二組則把「43歲男警總刑毀」案被告三項罪名的刑期結合，錯誤描述其刑事毀壞罪刑期；第三組更錯誤指「24歲男投擲麻包袋」案被告「襲警」，事實上被告僅被控非法集結罪。<br />\n<br />\n  何俊堯審理案件 圖1列為「同樣案情」案件<br />\n第一組案件 案情︰公聽會期間離座抗議 V. 案情︰遊行後在立法會外聚集，衝擊警方防線<br />\n罪名︰違反《立法會（權力及特權）條例》的行政指令 V. 罪名︰非法集結／非法集結及襲警<br />\n第二組案件 案情︰在警總外牆寫上「condom」及「con」V. 案情︰參與非法集結、向警察吐口水及噴黑玻璃門<br />\n罪名︰刑事毀壞 V. 罪名︰襲警、刑事毀壞及非法集結<br />\n第三組案件 案情︰萬聖節期間向馬路中心投擲兩個麻包袋 V. 案情︰從後推跌一名警長<br />\n罪名︰非法集結 V. 罪名︰襲警<br />\n圖1含有錯誤及誤導資訊，意圖指控裁判官何俊堯判刑較同類案件輕，屬誤導內容。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9-%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94%E5%9C%96%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%8A%E5%A0%AF%E8%BC%95%E5%88%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoG%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=17af5348\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&h=6a28e2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9-%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94%E5%9C%96%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%8A%E5%A0%AF%E8%BC%95%E5%88%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"00529bad0641838c111d599d19e459e99c7cbd87","tid":2181048,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f0f7a38fc811f458b46921440f2523c504deec","tid":2181048,"uid":305767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢不如話<br />\n<br />\n高尚情操 VS 蓄意傷人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個就真偏頗啦"},{"pid":"2d0c2b08cb15515bb7fd09d7480ee74296c284c5","tid":2181048,"uid":60648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾藍屍得番老作<br />\n<br />\n賤種就係賤種<br />\n<br />\nd 支那人真係最不誠實"}]}